":964283,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T08:50:34.000Z","msg":"「幣少爺」黃鉦傑獲准保釋後，今午（18日）前往深水埗明哥的飯店購買飯票，至約3時許駕乘私家車離開，期間大批南亞裔人士及市民包圍私家車，有市民不斷大嗌：「Money，Money！」情況十分混亂，需要警方在場驅趕。期間，一名自稱「Dragon Heart（龍心）」的男子，意外跌倒，眼鏡碎裂，相機亦損毀，他離開時連聲問:&quot;Why give money to the public is illegal! why, why!&quot;（點解向公眾派錢係犯法！點解，點解！)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181218/photo/bkn-20181218154105537-1218_00822_001_06b.jpg?20181218183103\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181218%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181218154105537-1218_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20181218183103&h=1605e929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批南亞人高呼：「Money, Money！」（陳賜慧攝)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181218/bkn-20181218154105537-1218_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=4028834767a5895d0167b0f59b6d06a4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181218%2Fbkn-20181218154105537-1218_00822_001.html%3Feventsection%3Dhk_news%26eventid%3D4028834767a5895d0167b0f59b6d06a4&d=AJX8bMqZTjfy%2B7WImQUbqJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=766c8a38\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181218/bkn-20181218154105537-1218_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=4028834767a5895d0167b0f59b6d06a4</a>"},{"pid":"be3f97127dee734c7f404e05c94ad53dc7f0ef36","tid":964283,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"龍心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ecaea23585e060c9d9b4ea657cf9f4c64ade86","tid":964283,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T08:52:57.000Z","msg":"捐左星火同郭卓堅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea0505b32d5460cbbc3d6be6609af150b4a49ab","tid":964283,"uid":57376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:24:35.00